gENROU.PMECH0.comment: Initial value of machine electrical power (pu, machine base)

gENROU.PSIppd0.comment: d-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

gENROU.PSIppq0.comment: q-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

gENROU.dsat.comment: To include saturation of during initialization

gENROU.ii0.comment: Imaginary component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

gENROU.ir0.comment: Real component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

gENROU.p0.comment: Initial active power generation (pu, machine base)

gENROU.q0.comment: Initial reactive power generation (pu, machine base)

gENROU.vr0.comment: Real component of initial terminal voltage

sCRX.T_AT_B.comment: Ratio between regulator numerator (lead) and denominator (lag) time constants

sCRX.T_E.comment: Excitation power source output time constant

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.a[1].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.a[2].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.b[1].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.b[2].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.x_start[1].comment: Initial or guess values of states

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.y_start.comment: Initial value of output (derivatives of y are zero up to nx-1-th derivative)

sCRX.r_cr_fd.comment: Ratio between crowbar circuit resistance and field circuit resistance

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.initType.comment: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.na.comment: Size of Denominator of transfer function.

sCRX.imLeadLag.TF.nb.comment: Size of Numerator of transfer function.

sCRX.C_SWITCH.comment: Feeding selection. False for bus fed, and True for solid fed
